title: Jamie Foxx Showed Diddy How To Party On A Budget | Colbert Classic
description:
After attending Diddy's million-dollar party, Jamie Foxx showed the rap mogul that a party could thrown on a budget, as long as there's an A-list crowd of up-and-comers in attendance. Stephen also found out the benefits of his stage name, Jamie Foxx, versus his birth name, Eric Marlon Bishop, and how he first got the bug for show business.
